title: Modern Stainless Steel One Bedroom with City View
posting_body: ['Modern Stainless Steel One Bedroom with City View', 'Listing ID #: 212970', 'Price: $2,650', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.0', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Pets: Pets OK', 'Apartment Amenities', 'City View', 'Dishwasher', 'Light', 'Renovated', 'Newly updated modern one bedroom/one bath located on 21st St.', 'The kitchen comes equipped with white cabinets, stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher.', 'Bathroom comes equipped with subway tiles and large white soaking tub.', 'Enjoy the city view with tons of natural light throughout the apartment.', 'The bedroom can accommodate a queen size bed and comes with its own closet.', "Located directly across from the Broadway Shopping Center where you'll find the post office, supermarket, dry cleaners, bank, and other stores for your convenience.", 'The q69 bus stop is located right at the corner of the building, the N/W subway lines are just a few blocks away.', 'Contact Sofia at <URL> to schedule for tour today!', 'Sofia Aguirre', 'Phone: (718) 685-2775', 'Mobile: (718) 424-0813', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 (718) 685-2775 \xa0 (718) 424-0813 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Sofia Aguirre at (718) 424-0813']
